      <body>
        
     
      <div xml:id="TheBlackArt"> 
              <interpGrp type="poembox">
                <interp ana="#form" type="free"></interp>
                <interp ana="#tone" type="other"></interp>
                <interp ana="#topic" type="society"></interp>
              </interpGrp>
             <lg> 
        <l>A woman who writes feels too much,</l>
               <l>those trances and portents!</l>
               <l>As if cycles and children and islands</l>
               <l>weren't enough; as if mourners and gossips</l>
               <l>and vegetables were never enough.</l>
               <l>She thinks she can warn the stars.</l>
               <l>A writer is essentially a spy.</l>
               <l>Dear love, I am that girl.</l>
             </lg>
            </div>
        
